Use case : Designing a cafe like Starbucks.
    1. Customers can order bevarages like Espresso/DarkRoast
    2. For any bevarage, customer can opt for any number of flavours like Milk, Mocha, Soy
    3. Each bevarage is available in 3 different options Tall, Medium, Small and costs can vary accordingly.
    4. Cost of the additional condiment depends on the size of the bevarage glass.

Features to be exposed.
    a. Provide the description of the order.
    b. Provide the cost of the order.

